The '''Ghana Davis Cup team''' represents [[Ghana]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Ghana Tennis Association]]. They have not competed since [[2015 Davis Cup|2015]].
They competed in Group I in [[1990 Davis Cup|1990]].
==History== Ghana competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1988 Davis Cup|1988]].
