'''South Africa's Strongest Man''' is an annual [[Strongman (strength athlete)|strongman]] competition held in [[South Africa]] and features primarily South African strength athletes.<ref name=autogenerated1>[http://www.davidhorne-gripmaster.com/strongmanresults.html David Horne's World of Grip<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> [[Gerrit Badenhorst]] and [[Ettiene Smit]] has now won the title 8 times.<ref name=autogenerated1 />
